## Tor Relay Configuration file

## SOCKS proxy port, configured to run only as a relay
SOCKSPort 0

################ Relay Information #####################

## Default port to advertise for incoming Tor connections
ORPort 9001

# Throttle traffic to 100KB/s (800Kbps)
RelayBandwidthRate 100 KBytes

## Set a maximum of 40 gigabytes each way per period.
AccountingMax 40 GBytes

## Each period starts on the 3rd of the month at 15:00
AccountingStart month 3 15:00

# Port to advertise for directory connections
DirPort 9030
